00:52:41.610 --> 00:52:43.840
Don't start with yourself.

00:52:43.840 --> 00:52:44.830
No, truly.

00:52:44.830 --> 00:52:46.892
The principle of loving
kindness practice,

00:52:46.892 --> 00:52:49.350
where instead of gathering our
attention around the feeling

00:52:49.350 --> 00:52:51.500
of the breath, we're
gathering our attention

00:52:51.500 --> 00:52:55.590
around the silent repetition
