00:52:57.810 --> 00:53:00.710
Or may you be happy,
something like that.

00:53:00.710 --> 00:53:04.030
And the principle,
classically, is

00:53:04.030 --> 00:53:07.820
that it's supposed to be done
in the easiest way possible.

00:53:07.820 --> 00:53:12.806
And the reality is that
starting with ourselves, which

00:53:12.806 --> 00:53:14.680
is how you're supposed
to start, because it's

00:53:14.680 --> 00:53:17.630
said to be easiest,
is not always easiest.

00:53:17.630 --> 00:53:20.130
Sometimes it's
really, really hard.

00:53:20.130 --> 00:53:22.990
So I always go back to
that fundamental principle

00:53:22.990 --> 00:53:24.970
of doing it in the
easiest way possible.

00:53:24.970 --> 00:53:28.250
Because part of what's
developing along

00:53:28.250 --> 00:53:31.350
with the loving kindness
is confidence and clarity.

00:53:31.350 --> 00:53:33.050
It's understanding
the difference

00:53:33.050 --> 00:53:37.840
between maybe having compassion
for someone else and giving in.

00:53:37.840 --> 00:53:40.650
Or understanding what it
feels like to have compassion

00:53:40.650 --> 00:53:43.080
for yourself and someone else.

00:53:43.080 --> 00:53:46.530
Or, there's a lot that is
developing all along the way,

00:53:46.530 --> 00:53:52.380
and so it's worth
not struggling.

00:53:52.380 --> 00:53:54.470
It doesn't mean you
never include yourself,

00:53:54.470 --> 00:53:55.440
because you have to.

00:53:55.440 --> 00:53:57.475
But it doesn't have
to be right away.

00:53:57.475 --> 00:53:58.225
It really doesn't.

